usdFileTransferAgentV1.name: usdFileTransferAgentV1
usdFileTransferAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the File Transfer component of the Unisphere Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the File Transfer component was
        supported in the Unisphere RX 1.x system releases.
usdFileTransferAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the File System application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when remote user information was removed and router name was added.

usdFileTransferAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the File System application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
